text: Anna Hilton ( Hermann, born 17 February 1963) is a Swedish equestrian. She competed in the individual eventing at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Sweden Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Lidingö Municipality
